name: Pirsus Artstation
description:
This model is based on oil painting.

I did not pursue the goal of repeating the style of a certain artist or direction in art. I wanted to get a drawing effect with a rich color palette so that this model could be used to create book illustrations.

Trained on VAE - 840000
